title: Happy New Year
lyrics:
The year of this, the year of that
Last year was the year of it all
I said it all would happen but it ain't
I guess I got my years wrong
Ain't nothing worse than a broken promise
'Cause you promised we would go to times square

But we didn't even make it to December

So I still never went there



I prolly been, to over and over again

Over and over again

Guess I'll be blowing with the wind

Over and over again like

Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh

Over and over again

Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh

Over and over again

Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh

Over and over again
